comments: Okogie (MIN) makes incidental contact with the part of Porzingis's (DAL) hand on the ball when he dislodges it during his jump shot attempt.
Richardson (DAL) reaches in and marginal contact occurs with Okogie's (MIN) arm as he dislodges the ball from him.
Okogie (MIN) cleanly deflects the pass attempt to Porzingis (DAL).
Porzingis (DAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Edwards' (MIN) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Edwards (MIN) makes contact to Doncic's (DAL) arm during his upward shooting motion and the contact affects his driving shot attempt.
Finney-Smith (DAL) and Beasley (MIN) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) places his hand on the ball during Beasley's (MIN) upward shooting motion and slides his hand off contesting his shot attempt at the rim.
Richardson (DAL) places an arm against Rubio (MIN) with no extension as he releases from contact.
Rubio (MIN) briefly places his hand to Richardson's (DAL) arm and quickly removes it during his drive to the basket.
Vanderblit (MN) and Kleber (DAL) engage and disengage with one another off ball.
Vanderbilt (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in Finney-Smith's (DAL) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Okogie (MIN) commits a take foul on Richardson (DAL).
Finney-Smith (DAL) brushes Edwards' (MIN) arm during his dunk attempt.
